      ],
      "source": "https://villagenhpny.gov/the-origins-of-new-hyde-park/"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "Long Island Jewish Hospital, founded in 1954, grew into Northwell Health’s nucleus and now sits on New Hyde Park’s northern edge.",
